ffmpeg: ffmpeg (A AV converter, streaming server and player)
ffmpeg:
ffmpeg: FFmpeg is a complete solution to record, convert and stream audio
ffmpeg: and video. The command line tool can convert fast from one video
ffmpeg: file format to another. It also supports grabbing and encoding in
ffmpeg: real time from a TV card. There is an HTTP multimedia streaming
ffmpeg: server for live broadcasts as well as a simple media player based
ffmpeg: on SDL and on the FFmpeg libraries.
ffmpeg:
